Hoʻokumu ʻia i ka makahiki 1949, a kūʻai ʻia a kūʻai ʻia e Hasbro i ka makahiki 1952, ʻo Mr. Potato Head he mea pāʻani ʻAmelika i loaʻa i ka ʻuala plastik a me nā ʻāpana plastik hiki ke hoʻopili ʻia, e like me nā pepeiao a me nā maka, e hana i kahi maka. ʻO ia ka mea pāʻani mua i hoʻolaha ʻia ma ke kīwī. [107]

I Iune, 1992 ma Muñoz Rivera Elementary School spelling bee ma Trenton, New Jersey, ua hāʻawi ʻia ka Hope Peresidena ʻAmelika ʻo Dan Quayle i kahi kāleka flash i kuhi hewa ʻole i ka "ʻuala" ma ke ʻano he "uala" a laila hoʻoikaika i kahi haumāna 12 makahiki e hoʻololi. kona huaolelo pololei. [108] [109] [110] ʻO kēia hanana ke kumu o ka hoʻohenehene ākea.